			<h4><a id="comment_link_64568859" name="comment_link_64568859" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23364041&amp;cid=64568859" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64568859)" >Re:No; the legislature can't change this court rul</a>


